    <p>{`The Vector `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`datadog_metrics`}</inlineCode>{` sink
`}<a parentName="p" {...{
        "href": "#buffers--batches"
      }}>{`batches`}</a>{` `}<a parentName="p" {...{
